OL,3,CAirline launches aptitude tests in bid
OL,4,Cto encourage more female pilots
OL,6,FWATCH: ITV Meridian's Sally Simmonds
OL,7,Fhas been to meet two pilots and try
OL,8,Fthe controls of a simulator at their
OL,9,Ftraining base in Crawley.
OL,11,FThe UK's biggest airline, easyJet, is
OL,12,Flaunching a new campaign to encourage
OL,13,Fmore female pilots and first officers
OL,14,Finto the aviation industry.
OL,16,FFewer than 10% are currently women and
OL,17,Fmore than half of British adults still
OL,18,Fbelieve a pilot is a job for a man.
