OL,3,CAirline launches aptitude tests in bid
OL,4,Cto encourage more female pilots
OL,6,FThe airline, which is Gatwick's
OL,7,Fbiggest, has rolled out two online
OL,8,Ftests so more people can 'find their
OL,9,Fwings'.
OL,11,FThe new aptitude tests assess some of
OL,12,Fthe key skills needed to become an
OL,13,Fairline pilot and has been designed to
OL,14,Fencourage more people to consider the
OL,15,Fcareer.
OL,17,FAnyone can take the test, as they aim
OL,18,Fto attract 200 more to the profession
OL,19,Fthis spring.
