OL,3,CAirline launches aptitude tests in bid
OL,4,Cto encourage more female pilots
OL,6,FIt's the first time the airline has
OL,7,Frun such a recruitment campaign as
OL,8,Fthey aim to dispel preconceived ideas
OL,9,Fabout the qualifications needed on the
OL,10,Fflight deck.
OL,12,FThe two online tests are for and .
OL,14,FThe company employs 4000 pilots of
OL,15,Fwhich 300 are women, which is about
OL,16,F7.5%. That's slightly higher than the
OL,17,FBritish average of 6.5% but the
OL,18,Findustry is keen to diversify.
