OL,3,CAirline launches aptitude tests in bid
OL,4,Cto encourage more female pilots
OL,6,FQualifying to be a pilot takes about
OL,7,Ftwo years including ground school
OL,8,Ftraining, simulator flying, single
OL,9,Fengine flying and supervised flying
OL,10,Fand pilots retrain every 6 months.
OL,12,FeasyJet Captain Sarah Ackerley, said:
OL,13,F"Tackling gender stereotyping within
OL,14,Faviation has been a long-standing
OL,15,Fmission for easyJet and I'm excited to
OL,16,Fbe part of this latest campaign that's
OL,17,Fallowing people to get a real insight
OL,18,Finto what skills are really important
OL,19,Fto do this job, and encourage more
OL,20,Fwomen into the profession.
